static int32_t DPU_DopplerProcHWA_configEdma ( DPU_DopplerProcHWA_Obj *  obj,
DPU_DopplerProcHWA_Config *  cfg 
)
inlinestatic

Description
Doppler DPU EDMA configuration. This implementation of doppler processing involves Ping/Pong Mechanism, hence there are two sets of EDMA transfer.

Parameters
[in]obj- DPU obj
[in]cfg- DPU configuration
Return values
EDMAerror code, see EDMA API.
